race.comment: SILVERTREE BEN (1) has shown good improvement at his last two starts, hitting the frame latest when 3rd at this track over 300m. Won at his only start from this draw. Deserves serious consideration. PATH TO NIRVANA (2) has been hard to follow lately, running seventh (20.01) last time but prior to that ran very well when placed at this track. Well placed here and should do much better. IRISH BREW (3) has mixed form recently, finishing fourth (19.99) in a Grade 5 at this track latest but did run well two back when in the frame. Expected to do much better this time. DUNSMORE FLYER (7) was out of the money at this circuit last start but can make amends.
